com.ociweb.pronghorn.pipe.schema.loader

Class DictionaryFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ociweb.pronghorn.pipe.schema.loader.DictionaryFactory

  • public class DictionaryFactory
extends Object
    Holds count of how many of each type of field is required and what the default values are. Default(initial) values are sparse so only the index and the value are kept in this class. Upon request this class will generate the needed dictionary arrays fully populated.
    Author:
    Nathan Tippy
